🧪 10-second “micro-switch” (after a few reps)

Once practiced, you can compress it to:
	•	Posture up → 2 quick 4/4 breaths → slight tension → lift gaze
	•	Cue: “Up… forward… open.”
	•	Exhale long (6–8) → “steady”

That’s it.

